</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center">“惨叫声此起彼伏，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">伤亡情况十分严重”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201116/1c4aea719a2743d2a09867c0649c827c.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">据马西斯邮报报道，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>阿塞拜疆在纳卡地区</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>悍然动用明令禁止的白磷弹！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201116/38211e352bc34b1da0d31256a3b65a96.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">在这场持续已久的混乱之下，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">无数无辜的平民流离失所，住宅受到炮火的洗礼；</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201116/4580a016c8f54787bede11b449fe9781.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">大量的士兵遭到导弹的袭击、阵亡场面尸横遍野...</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201116/05fdd97953b342bbaacbb3e1e52d3bfd.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201116/0f6f051eaae1417a8ab59b177ff1f05f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201116/c1c685eda4ee4cf7849a877f28a3c9e2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">即便是在多方多次的调停之下，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">战火依旧没有停息...</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而就在今天，环球网报道，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>印度和巴基斯坦，</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>也突发了大规模的炮战！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201116/a8d64027c46547a6ad94d93f5ed06464.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201116/56f271ee16e244a99696cab68bde466a.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">就在上个月月底，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">阿塞拜疆突然袭击了纳卡地区亚美尼亚驻地。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201116/bbfe4e1bd8ca4b12919fd4f26dfa537e.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">一时间，大批白磷弹从同天女散花一般从天而降，在空中爆裂。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201116/bd99dfca45f94726b67df26340a0e816.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201116/d60286b72f8f48c4aa8d2eefc28de938.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>整个山头被点燃，</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>燃起的熊熊大火染红了半边天！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201116/92be2ec1fa7f48b2a2f80ce22a5a6e9b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">白磷弹的燃点十分低，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">不仅在普通的温度下就能燃烧，还可以释放出<strong>1000度的高温</strong>。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201116/4bd0d8a0b3bc4d58adea753d2d2fde76.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201116/453946ce39a2456392a8844ab04dcff5.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">图片：来自网络</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">火焰不仅很难扑灭，附着性很强。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">如果附着到人体的皮肤上，皮肉都能穿透下去，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>一直烧下去，甚至能烧到骨头！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201116/f6b310c3543a41a08aa31005577abeea.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201116/6cdeed96c4d64daa8bdd2b279ec13d0f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">白磷弹在燃烧时还会释放大量白色烟雾。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201116/ab7c55d62fad4dc5887cd582a5499e5a.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">图片：来自网络</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这些白色烟雾还有五氧化二磷，是一种剧毒的物质！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">和水再次发生反应后，能释放大量的热量，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>对人体各类器官将造成严重的灼烧！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201116/7d6cd6df79c0488b99c5a0690989d15f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">正是因为过于可怕的威力，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">白磷弹已经被国际条约列为明令禁止使用的违禁武器。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201116/3ddc89ef549542d1bedf67169186593f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>这种武器，</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>成了撒向战场上空的“恐怖烟花”...</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201116/e6c66041678f4449b2f5d6a319f30532.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">再看看这样的视频画面：</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>（以下画面含有一定的血腥场面，请谨慎观看）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201116/05fdd97953b342bbaacbb3e1e52d3bfd.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201116/9123f97b96e74651971633a98d8e354a.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">一段段无人机空袭的场景中，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">枪林弹雨之下，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">有些正在休息的士兵被直接轰飞；</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201116/5bce5a8a25514b12bdc26b71a1927300.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">有的士兵没有掩体遮挡，绝望逃命，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">最后在轰炸瞬间遗体四散；</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201116/345800376e0a41cbbd9c18e57ba92873.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">大量的士兵不幸阵亡，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">他们浑身是血、横七竖八地流落荒野；</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201116/3c1e17c3d3304c4db359337008de7353.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201116/910380f2911548beadf6231d79120cbf.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">原来战争，就是这么地残酷无情...</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201116/472b2514f6af42c192e42c8321c13385.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">从今年开始，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">亚美尼亚和阿塞拜疆之间的军事冲突，已经陆陆续续持续了2个多月了。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">而在此期间，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2国冲突一触即发，</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>局势进一步失控！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201116/dc0fa1017cb247a0b79bf4f15b3b2dc0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看似离我们很遥远的战争，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>已经真实在上演了！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">亚美尼亚政府正式宣布：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>全国开展戒严令，</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>军事总动员发布！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201116/4724999d55c4453cbb8b54664d7f980b.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201116/4f457f6a80b044bd85578b6b34bc145e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">随着战况的升级，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">双方甚至动用了大规模的杀伤性武器！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201116/eb5abe8502df4a989f3f7be64cccd30f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">同时，他们也互相指责对方加剧了局势升级。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">两国的争议地带——纳卡地区，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">遭受了无数次炮火的洗礼，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>成了一座人间炼狱。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201116/5190afaa0b89417daa7b0f281c0650b7.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201116/3b04d8b210244dc2ab823db5cafd4c9f.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">战火不只是波及到了边境地带，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">同时也殃及了更多无辜的人...</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>阿塞拜疆第二大城市占贾市</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>遭受了无差别攻击。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201116/4580a016c8f54787bede11b449fe9781.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201116/a1a477eef90b49bbb255f1e033c9c2de.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">炸弹无差别地袭击了<strong>平民区</strong>！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201116/787d8ce6f2954831998a1820e046ed26.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>国际条约眀令禁止</strong>的集束弹、白磷弹，纷纷出现！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">如此危险的物品，甚至还能在大街小巷内<strong>随处可见</strong>。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201116/c218679e1227490296deee5269be747e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201116/359abecd79714067a7b7c0477f163f3f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">近半数的民众，被迫流离失所。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201116/66b6d9fda34644da949404f99119b63a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">纳卡地区首府也接连遭受炮击，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>这个城市几乎</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>成了一座“鬼城”！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201116/43445e6bcb6445a7a04be7205065d11c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">平民区的住宅大楼，在顷刻间被炸得<strong>满目疮痍.</strong>..</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201116/640b6ea88fb944f69b0f9039bc7437f1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201116/22801e6268904554b2e111dd11fd8c87.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">还有多名战俘被抓后，遭到了非人的虐待。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">有的被逼下跪，<strong>连老人都不放过，</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201116/052155b8d20e4297bc661d0c83d52543.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">有的被拽倒在地、用枪指头，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">还有的战俘身上裹着亚美尼亚国旗后，惨遭射杀。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201116/bb95b02d8f95434c94c6ebca316cd114.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2国在俄罗斯的调解之下，达成了短暂的共识：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">遵守人道主义停火协议！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可万万没想到的是，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>就在协议生效的4分钟后，</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>双方便发生冲突、撕破协议！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201116/f37e71b63bc1430f80f1c3278c85ec0c.png" max-width="600" /></p>
