<p>Coby性格很皮，没事就喜欢偷吃零食，反正闲着也是闲着；</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201116/8d5c2717daac4d52808df033765c27a5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
